# Build-context exclusions for the P2-v3 images (docker/web, docker/ui).
#
# WITHOUT this file `COPY . /app` in docker/web/Dockerfile drags the ENTIRE repo
# into the build context — including retest_runs/ (multi-GB raw disk images),
# sessions/, and .git — which both bloats the image and can fill the Docker VM
# disk ("no space left on device" mid-build). Keep this list tight.

# ── version control / tooling ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.github
.claude
*.md
docs/

# ── Python caches / venvs / build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
*.egg-info/
build/
dist/

# ── runtime / data that must NEVER be baked into an image ─────────────────────
# huge: raw disk images, recovered artifacts, per-run worker workspaces
retest_runs/
sessions/
data/
*.img
*.qcow2
*.raw

# ── node (the web image doesn't need the UI tree; the ui image has its own ctx)─
node_modules/
apps/web/ui/.next/
apps/web/ui/node_modules/

# ── local scratch / secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
*.log
.DS_Store
docs/_local/
